ggimage, ggplotifyyyplotmsa

require(msa)
require(seqinr)
require(yyplot)
require(pheatmap)
require(cowplot)

## fasta
mySequenceFile <- system.file("examples", "exampleAA.fasta", package="msa")
mySequences <- readAAStringSet(mySequenceFile)

## 
myFirstAlignment <- msa(mySequences)
## use default substitution matrix
## 
myAlignment <- msaConvert(myFirstAlignment, type="seqinr::alignment")
d <- dist.alignment(myAlignment, "identity")

## NJ
require(ape)
tree <- nj(d)

## 
require(ggtree)
p1 <- ggtree(tree, layout='circular') + geom_tiplab2(size=3, offset=.1) + xlim(-.2, 3) 

## 
dd <- as.matrix(d)
p2 = pheatmap(dd, show_colnames=F, silent=TRUE)

## 
p3 <- msaPrettyPlot(myFirstAlignment, y=c(164, 213),
    showNames="left", shadingMode="functional",
    shadingModeArg="structure", 
    askForOverwrite=FALSE) 

plot_grid(
  plot_grid(p1, p2$gtable, ncol=2, rel_widths=c(.6, 1), labels=LETTERS[1:2]),
  p3, ncol=1, labels=c("", "C"))
